reviewText: If you are into tentacle anime then this hentai is definitely for you

Everyone has heard of The Sailor Scouts, now meet The Venus 5, they are the Hentai version of Sailor Moon, which means this film is only recommended for Adult viewers. Similar but different, there are monsters with tentacles involved here so anyone into monsters, check this out. And let's not forget the cat in this Anime, he is a total pervert. Enjoy
Not a bad hentai movie at all, although the part with the cat was a little disturbing.  All in all though a good choice for a hentai fan, and who isn't a hentai fan?
If you like sailor moon, give this dvd a try. There doesn't seem to be much of a plot, but all the "Hentai" makes up for it, hehe
